          <div class="callout-label">⚡ TL;DR — Pick by job</div>
          <p><strong>Done-for-you SEO publishing:</strong> theStacc — blog + landing pages, drafted and live. <strong>Pure article volume:</strong> Byword. <strong>Multi-format marketing copy:</strong> Copy.ai or Jasper. <strong>Product descriptions at scale:</strong> Writesonic. <strong>Cheapest credible generator:</strong> SEOWriting.ai at $19/mo.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Skip the asset shuffle.</h4>
            <p>theStacc generates and publishes SEO blog and landing pages — drafted, on-page, and live. <strong>$99/mo Content SEO.</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">Book a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · No pitch deck</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="what-is">What is a "bulk content generation" tool?</h2>
