          <li><strong>Done-for-you platforms</strong> — theStacc. Generates SEO blogs and landing pages and ships them live to your CMS.</li>
        </ol>

        <div class="callout callout-warn">
          <div class="callout-label">⚠️ Watch for these traps</div>
          <p>Avoid tools that <strong>(a)</strong> charge "per word" with no upper limit, <strong>(b)</strong> claim "multi-format" but only output text snippets, or <strong>(c)</strong> hide brand-voice training behind enterprise pricing.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="how-we-tested">How we tested all 10 tools</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Brief</strong> — same 50 keywords, 100 product SKUs, 20 ad sets, brand voice provided.</li>
          <li><strong>Industries</strong> — DTC e-commerce, B2B SaaS, local services.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — quality score, per-asset cost, time-to-publish, brand voice consistency.</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $2,310 across all ten platforms.</li>
        </ul>

